17
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:19,720
of the object's momentum to energy - or pcover E. If your momentum increases, p times

18
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:24,250
c gets closer and closer to equaling yourenergy, so their ratio gets closer and closer

19
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:28,830
to being one, and your speed gets closer andcloser to light speed. But because of that

20
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:32,860
tiny little bit of mass, the momentum sideof the triangle will always be a little bit

21
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:37,420
